href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Pale_Ale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Pale Ale is one of the options for the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Orange.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/24px-Bundle_Orange.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/36px-Bundle_Orange.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Brewer.27s_Bundle\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Brewer's Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Pantry\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Pantry (Remixed)</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Pale_Ale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Pale Ale can be used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <a href=\"/File:Shirt138.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt138.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Shirt138.png/24px-Shirt138.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e4/Shirt138.png 1.5x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Black Leather Jacket</a>. It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Pale_Ale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a> requests a Pale Ale by mail on the 14th of <a href=\"/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a> in the <a href=\"/Quests#Pam_Is_Thirsty\" title=\"Quests\">\"Pam Is Thirsty\" quest</a>.  The reward is <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"350\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />350g</span> and 1 <a href=\"/Friendship\" title=\"Friendship\">Friendship</a> heart.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Pale_Ale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Added ability to age inside <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">casks</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Can now be purchased at <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a> • <a href=\"/Green_Tea\" title=\"Green Tea\">Green Tea</a> • <a href=\"/Juice\" title=\"Juice\">Juice</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil\" title=\"Oil\">Oil</a> • <a href=\"/Truffle_Oil\" title=\"Truffle Oil\">Truffle Oil</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Aged_Roe\" title=\"Aged Roe\">Aged Roe</a> • <a href=\"/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\">Caviar</a> • <a href=\"/Jellies_and_Pickles\" title=\"Jellies and Pickles\">Jellies and Pickles</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414031353\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.192 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.219 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3988/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 81558/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3634/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 11728/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.014/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.19 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  120.935      1 -total\n 75.60%   91.429      1 Temp