      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Pale Ale\n|source      = <nowiki />\n*[[Artisan Goods]]\n*[[Ginger Island#Island South|Ginger Island Resort]]\n|buff        = {{Name|Tipsy|link=Buffs#Tipsy{{!}}Tipsy}}{{Name|Speed|−1}}\n|buffduration= 30s\n|edibility   = 20\n|sellprice   = 300\n|ingredients = {{Name|Hops|1}}\n|craftingstation = {{Name|Keg}}\n|crafttime   = 2250m (37.5h)\n}}\n'''Pale Ale''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made from the [[Keg]] using [[Hops]], taking 1-2 days. It is also available at the [[Ginger Island#Island South|Ginger Island Resort]] for {{Price|1000}}. [[Pam]] sells Pale Ale in her [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|30|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s. When consumed, Pale Ale causes a [[Buffs|Tipsy]] buff that decreases [[Speed]] by 1.\n\n==Aged Values==\nPale Ale can be placed inside a [[Cask]] to age from normal quality to silver, gold, and eventually iridium quality. Iridium quality doubles the base sell price of Pale Ale.  \n\nNormal, silver, and gold quality Pale Ale can be prematurely removed from a cask at any time by striking the cask with an [[Axes|Axe]], [[Hoes|Hoe]], or [[Pickaxes|Pickaxe]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Normal Quality\n!Silver Quality<br />(x 1.25)\n!Gold Quality<br />(x 1.5)\n!Iridium Quality<br />(x 2)\n|-\n|{{Qualityprice|Pale Ale|300|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Pale Ale|300|quality=silver|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 9 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Pale Ale|300|quality=gold|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 8 Days<br />Total: 17 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Pale Ale|300|quality=iridium|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 17 Days<br />Total: 34 Days''\n|-\n|}\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n|hate=Sebastian,Penny,Jas,Vincent,Leo\n|love=Pam\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nPale Ale is one of the options for the {{Bundle|brewers||y}}.\n\n==Tailoring==\nPale Ale can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[File:Shirt138.png|24px]] [[Tailoring|Black Leather Jacket]]. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\n*[[Pam]] requests a Pale Ale by mail on the 14th of [[Summer]] in the [[Quests#Pam Is Thirsty|\"Pam Is Thirsty\" quest]].  The reward is {{Price|350}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.1|Added ability to age inside [[cask]]s.}}\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.5|Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.}}\n{{History|1.6|Can now be purchased at [[Desert Festival]].}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Helles Bier]]\n[[es:Cerveza pálida]]\n[[fr:Bière blonde]]\n[[it:Malto chiaro]]\n[[ja:ペールエール]]\n[[ko:페일 에일]]\n[[hu:Világos sör]]\n[[pt:Pale Ale]]\n[[ru:Светлый эль]]\n[[tr:Soluk Bira]]\n[[zh:淡啤酒]]"
